### Tenant Service API Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/registration
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 1. Create Tenant
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": "acme-corp",
